(44, 11, 27, 49, 4, 11, 11, 'prophets', 'Connection of Prophets in Scripture', 'This connection highlights the role of prophets in the early church. Both passages emphasize the importance of prophets as part of the ministry structure.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 11, 27, 40, 23, 34, 34, 'prophets', 'Connection of Prophets and Persecution', 'Both passages emphasize the role of prophets. Acts 11:27 mentions prophets coming to Antioch, while Matthew 23:34 speaks of sending prophets who will face persecution.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 11, 27, 44, 2, 17, 17, 'prophets from Jerusalem', 'Connection of Prophecy and Spirit', 'Both passages emphasize the role of prophets and the outpouring of the Spirit. Acts 2:17 speaks of prophesying in the last days, while Acts 11:27 mentions prophets coming to Antioch, indicating the fulfillment of this prophetic activity.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 11, 27, 46, 14, 32, 32, 'prophets', 'Connection of Prophets in Scripture', 'This connection highlights the role of prophets in the early church. Both passages emphasize the authority and order among prophets, indicating that their spirits are subject to one another.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 11, 28, 44, 21, 10, 10, NULL, 'Connection of Agabus the Prophet', 'Both passages emphasize the role of Agabus as a prophet. In Acts 11:28, he predicts a famine, while in Acts 21:10, he is identified again as a prophet from Judea.', 'theme', 0.34199999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
